dcterms:description: The Kaggle dataset is collected from PersonalityCafe, a platform where people share their personality types and engage in daily communications. This dataset contains a total of 8675 users, with each user contributing 45-50 posts.

dcterms:description: Pandora is another dataset collected from Reddit, where personality labels are extracted from users’ self-introductions that contain MBTI types. This dataset contains dozens to hundreds of posts from each of the 9067 users.
dcterms:title: Pandora
